Package com.mvp4g.client.history

Interface Summary
HistoryConverter<E extends EventBus> Interface that defines methods to convert a token from/to an event.
HistoryProxy Interface to define methods needed to manage history

This interface is needed in order to test without using GWT History class.
NavigationConfirmationInterface Define an interface that allow to confirm or stop a navigation event.
 

Class Summary
ClearHistory This particular history converter will clear browse history from GWT token whenever an event to which it is associated is fired.
DefaultHistoryProxy  
NavigationEventCommand Command that represents a navigation event.This command is passed to the Navigation Confirmation object that may allow the navigation by executing this command.
PlaceService Place Service defines the connection between the application and the browser history.
